data.description: Wonderful 4-sided brick ranch on large level lot for under $350K! Home features open floor plan, master on main, hardwood floors, tile bath, separate laundry room, and room to grow. Kitchen has solid surface countertops, breakfast bar, custom tile backsplash and stainless steel appliances. Enclosed deck overlooks the nearly acre of private, fenced back yard. Tons of room to entertain or play. Minutes to East West Connector, shopping, schools and Cobb County Parks.
